title: KISLEV FORT SIEGE: REALM OF THE ICE QUEEN - Total War: WARHAMMER Mod Gameplay
description:
KISLEV FORT SIEGE: REALM OD THE ICE QUEEN - Total War: WARHAMMER Mod Gameplay - Today we got some awesome mods for our siege battle! We are using a map called Kislev Fort, and a Kislev faction mod. The fort is under attack by Norsca and Wintertooth.  Enjoy the Siege Battle :D

Map: http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1106419211&searchtext=Kislev
